history.content:
I Was wondering if the number we see on calcentral for waitlist is the same one that tells us what LAB waitlist position we are in.

All students who are on the waitlist for EE16B said that we are most likely on the waitlist because of lab. I don't want to be 16 position on the waitlist on calcentral, but be the next person off the waitlist for a specific lab. 

Are these numbers different? Is there a way to find my lab waitlist position.
history.subject: EE16B Lab Waitlist Position VS Class Waitlist Position
